Klooni1010 Privacy policy

This Privacy Policy has been created in order to disclose our information collection, use and disclosure practices for the application Kolooni! 10 10 puzzle game.
Kolooni! 10 10 puzzle game is an entertainment application, that allows users arrange bricks of different sizes and color shapes.
It'll take you back to your childhood with very nice graphics design for Brick game.This is a classic yet innovative game!.
Game interface is very friendly and simple to use for all users of all ages.
Simply Drag the blocks, and fill up all grids. 

All communication is between your mobile device and your the game.
We are not involved in this communication and as such do not collect any personal information.


We take seriously the security of all information associated with the app and take all reasonable precautions to protect this information.

Our App may contain links to other sites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or the content of these third party sites. 


By using the App, you signify your assent to our Privacy Policy. If you do not agree to this policy, please do not use the App. 
We reserve the right, at our discretion, to modify this policy at any time and would contact you if there's a change in policy.

